  <section class="readme-section">
    <h3>Issue : force git pull</h3>
    <pre>
      <code class="bash">
        ### between a branch and the master

        $> git fetch --all
            # downloads the latest from remote without trying to merge or rebase
        $> git reset --hard origin/master
            # reset : resets the master branch to what you just fetched
            # --hard : changes all files in your working tree to match files in master

        ### between two branches

        $> git reset --hard origin/your_branch

        ### Try to git pull again
      </code>
    </pre>
